Package org.eclipse.persistence.internal.sessions.factories

Class SessionsFactory

java.lang.Object
org.eclipse.persistence.internal.sessions.factories.SessionsFactory
Direct Known Subclasses:
XRSessionsFactory
public class SessionsFactory extends Object
INTERNAL: Builds EclipseLink Sessions from the XML Session Config model. Model classes that are not built, are processed only.
Version:
1.0
